      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 font-Futurewave">
        <h2
          class="text-xl font-bold sm:text-4xl nm-flat-stone-100-sm dark:nm-flat-gray-800-lg p-6"
        >
          From the Blog
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-8">
          My adventurous life as a developer in Japan.
        </p>
      </div>
